text: Henry Robinson (11 March 1864 - 24 March 1931) was an Australian cricketer. He played six first-class matches for New South Wales between 1889/90 and 1892/93. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1864 births Category:1931 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: Henry Robinson (New South Wales cricketer)
